    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-spec icon powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six independent throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise mechanical linkage, feeding power to the rear wheels through an M-Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight and the valvetrain is within factory tolerances, making this a mechanically sound example for the purist.",
