      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Toyota 4Runner TRD Off-Road in Classic Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features black SofTex seats that are firm and supportive, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it should, including the crawl control and multi-terrain select systems. Under the hood, the 4.0L V6 runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history at the local dealership. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The Bridgestone Dueler tires have plenty of life left, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next adventure.",
